SimpleAV aims on simplifing you job on decoding videos.
It is released under LGPL v3.

Current version is 0.1.0b, based on libav v0.7.

The next version may features:
 * precise seeking
 * correct down-mixing

Start with "saplayer-old.c" if you are interested. :-P
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
COMPILATION:

    simple run 'make' under this folder.

Then have fun!
